            "detailed_description": "<img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/830410/extras/rapto_mariet.jpg?t=1537792276\" ><br><br><strong>Nogalious</strong> is a pixel-art action adventure set in a medieval-themed universe with plenty of puzzles and menacing challenges. Take on the role of Nogalious, a former knight of the Kingdom of Rusadir, and explore 5 different worlds to save your daughter Mariet from the evil claws of Darama.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Classic 8-bit 2D platforming now on Steam</h2><strong>Nogalious</strong> brings back the magic of 8-bit computers to your PC! Originally released on MSX, Spectrum, Amstrad and Commodore 64, this brand new version on Steam adds more than 100 achievements and genuine retro playability.<br><br><img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/830410/extras/achiv.jpg?t=1537792276\" ><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Fight the malign forces of darkness</h2>Stop Darama, former right hand of King Alphan, from conquering the Kingdom of Rusadir. Beat the armies of minions commanded by 4 terrifying bosses –Zovach, Grotton, Harmor and Lordaf– and bring Mariet back home. As in classy adventures, use different objects and weapons to ruin Darama’s plans!<br><br><img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/830410/extras/the-weapons-v5.jpg?t=1537792276\" >",
            "about_the_game": "<img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/830410/extras/rapto_mariet.jpg?t=1537792276\" ><br><br><strong>Nogalious</strong> is a pixel-art action adventure set in a medieval-themed universe with plenty of puzzles and menacing challenges. Take on the role of Nogalious, a former knight of the Kingdom of Rusadir, and explore 5 different worlds to save your daughter Mariet from the evil claws of Darama.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Classic 8-bit 2D platforming now on Steam</h2><strong>Nogalious</strong> brings back the magic of 8-bit computers to your PC! Originally released on MSX, Spectrum, Amstrad and Commodore 64, this brand new version on Steam adds more than 100 achievements and genuine retro playability.<br><br><img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/830410/extras/achiv.jpg?t=1537792276\" ><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Fight the malign forces of darkness</h2>Stop Darama, former right hand of King Alphan, from conquering the Kingdom of Rusadir. Beat the armies of minions commanded by 4 terrifying bosses –Zovach, Grotton, Harmor and Lordaf– and bring Mariet back home. As in classy adventures, use different objects and weapons to ruin Darama’s plans!<br><br><img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/830410/extras/the-weapons-v5.jpg?t=1537792276\" >",
            "short_description": "Nogalious is a retro-style action platformer that pays homage to the era of classic 2D platforming on 8-bit personal computers. Explore 5 different worlds and go through cozy dungeons in the first title of a trilogy that tells the story of Nogalious, his daughter Mariet, and the evil Darama.",
            "supported_languages": "English, Spanish - Spain, French, German",
            "reviews": "“A great nostalgia trip, A game likes this really hits you in the childhood and runs with it. A solid 2D platformer full of difficult boss battles and clever level design. I could easily see this on my TV back in the day and it made me smile, Well in between all the swearing as like I say it is a bit difficult in places. InIts a short review as its a very clear-cut game, Its retro looking, Plays like a retro game and is worth your time.”<br>7.4 / 10 – <a href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/linkfilter/?url=http://www.gertlushgaming.co.uk/2018/08/10/review-nogalious-steam/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"  >GERT LUSH GAMING</a><br><br>“Si sois amantes de los videojuegos retro, os traemos una propuesta que no podréis rechazar.”<br><a href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/linkfilter/?url=https://www.hobbyconsolas.com/noticias/videojuego-espanol-retro-nogalious-ya-disponible-steam-289415?utm_content=bufferef430&amp;utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=Twitter&amp;utm_campaign=HI\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"  >HOBBY CONSOLAS</a><br><br>“Nogalious, é um game que te prende em todos os sentidos, fazendo com que você queira jogar mais e mais até finaliza-lo. Apesar de apresentar uma certa dificuldade em algumas fases, é um joga que da gosto de tentar novamente, porque em vez de te deixar nervoso com o desafio, ele te traz diversão e satisfação ao superar os seus limites e concluir os desafios.   Sou muito crítico quanto a jogos, mas quando o jogo é bom eu reconheço e esse mereceu nota máxima em nossa review. Parabéns LUEGOLU3GO STUDIOS, continuem nesse caminho que tem tudo pra dar certo.”<br>10 / 10 – <a href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/linkfilter/?url=https://jamgamesbrasil.blogspot.com/2018/08/review-nogalious-chronicles.html?m=1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"  >JAM GAMES BRASIL</a><br>",
            "header_image": "https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/830410/header.jpg?t=1537792276",
